  <sceneprops>
    <title> We're here to take care of people </title>
    <description>
      We met Gary Morsch, from Kansas City, and his brother Mark from Orlando,
      along with their small team of roving street medics
      from Heart to Heart, during the Republican Convention in Cleveland.
      Started by Gary twenty four
      years ago, Heart to Heart
      is a volunteer organization for serving people in need
      around the world following disasters or proactively at events like this.
    </description>
